        </Sectionhead>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-5">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
            A Little Background.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
            I started creating applications at the age of 16 on my Android phone ğŸ“± before I got my first computer (thanks, Mom, for the gift ğŸ). It was a wise investment, and today, I develop consumer-grade applications. Computer science is my primary field ğŸ’». Moreover, I pursued some studies in economics, which enabled me to create business management solutions. Today, I'm a full-stack developer, but after 3 years of experience, I specialized in frontend development ğŸŒ because it's the visible part of your application.
        </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
        {
            publishedTeamMembers.map((teamMemberEntry) => (
            <div class="group">
                <div class="w-full aspect-square">
                <Picture
                    src={teamMemberEntry.data.avatar.src}
